Use the standard library
This is how to tri of n:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this n times:
      Add result to i
      When i is at least 2, then:
         When remainder of i and 2 is 0, then:
            Add result to sqrt of (product of i and i)
         But, if not:
            Add result to tofloat of (product of i and i)
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know